presets.name: Release Notes 120625,1853
presets.text:
╔═───────────────────────────── Release Notes ─────────────────────────────═╗

    As you can guess, this ones a Mahjong game, but this time it's very
    different since 'beautiful' japanese girls show up each time you end a
    level, then you can use up & down cursors to scroll the images.

    I must admit that digitized VGA graphics and Adlib musics are very good!

    Unzip the 2 files into the same directory using PKUNZIP -D to install the
    game.

    Another fine quality release from SKiLLiON !!
    
  ╚═─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────═╝

presets.name: Release Notes 120625,1945
presets.text:
╔═───────────────────────────── Release Notes ─────────────────────────────═╗

    Ishar II is very similar to Ishar I. There aren't too many changes,
    but there are more characters, more scenery, better graphics, etc..

    If you like RPG's you shouldn't miss this one.

    Although the the game is in French, it is very playable.
    (At least it's more playable than Lost in Time.. ;)

    I've played the game for about one and a half hours and haven't
    found any protection yet. If there is, SKiLLiON will release a new
    crack/fix later on.

              Another fine quality release from SKiLLiON!

  ╚═─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────═╝
